title: Van Canto Discography (2006 - 2014)
description:
This is the complete discography of Van Canto as of 2014.

All albums/tracks ripped from my original copies.


[2006] [A Storm to Come]
- from the 2009 Napalm Records Re-Release

[2008] [Hero]
- also from the 2009 Napalm Records Re-Release
- contains one bonus track, previously unreleased

[2010] [Tribe of Force]
- the original 2010 release

[2011] [Break the Silence]
- the Limited Edition Digipack

[2014] [Dawn of the Brave]
- the Limited Mediabook Edition
- contains a Bonus Disc with orchestral and various other tracks

All files are 320 CBR mp3. Ripped with EAC.

Enjoy and support the band by buying their music if you enjoy it!
